    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Banned on some worlds, such as Ghorus Prime, these grenades selectively destroy plants and plant fiber without harming other biological matter, and theyâ€™re considered more tool than weapon in many circles. A defoliant grenade unleashes a cloud of rust-red dust that causes vegetation to wither and die on contact. This kills most mundane grasses, shrubs, vines, brambles, small trees, and other moderately thick vegetation, eliminating any difficult terrain caused by those features. Larger trees and wooden objects take full damage but typically are not destroyed outright. Creatures with the plant type take the listed damage and can attempt a Reflex save for half damage. All other creatures and objects are unaffected.</p>\n<table style=\"width: 74.9169%; height: 74px;\" border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 14.3613%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\"><strong>MODEL</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 13.417%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\"><strong>LEVEL</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.3754%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\"><strong>PRICE</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 58.5549%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\"><strong>EFFECT</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 14.3613%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Mk 1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 13.417%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.3754%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">75</td>\n<td style=\"width: 58.5549%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Explode (2d6 A, 15 ft.; see text)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 10px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 14.3613%; height: 10px; text-align: center;\">Mk 2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 13.417%; height: 10px; text-align: center;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.3754%; height: 10px; text-align: center;\">320</td>\n<td style=\"width: 58.5549%; height: 10px; text-align: center;\">Explode (3d6 A, 20 ft.; see text)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 14.3613%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Mk 3</td>\n<td style=\"width: 13.417%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">7</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.3754%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">850</td>\n<td style=\"width: 58.5549%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Explode (6d6 A, 20 ft.; see text)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 14.3613%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Mk 4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 13.417%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">12</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.3754%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">4,800</td>\n<td style=\"width: 58.5549%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Explode (10d6 A, 20 ft.; see text)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"
